issue_text: You must specify a valid value for AccessControl (SuperPrivate). Valid values are ["AuthenticatedRead", "AwsExecRead", "BucketOwnerFullControl", "BucketOwnerRead", "LogDeliveryWrite", "Private", "PublicRead", "PublicReadWrite"]
A bucket with AccessControl set should also have OwnershipControl configured
Consider using AWS::S3::BucketPolicy instead of AccessControl
Invalid Property Resources/MyS3Bucket/Properties/BucketNaming. Did you mean BucketName?
Invalid Property Resources/MyEC2Instance/Properties/InstanceTypez. Did you mean InstanceType?
